# CODEOWNERS — Factoría Standards template
# Purpose: enforce the Human Gates defined in AGENTS.md automatically.
# Replace @TECH-LEAD with the actual GitHub handle(s) on project setup.
#
# How it works: any PR touching these paths REQUIRES review from the
# listed owner before merge (with branch protection's "require review
# from Code Owners" enabled). This is Human Gate enforcement, not
# bureaucracy — everything NOT listed here flows with normal review.

# Schema changes — the irreversible layer
/migrations/                    @TECH-LEAD
/supabase/migrations/           @TECH-LEAD

# Authentication & authorization logic
/src/services/auth/             @TECH-LEAD

# RLS policies (if kept separate from migrations)
/policies/                      @TECH-LEAD

# The constitution itself and agent configuration
/AGENTS.md                      @TECH-LEAD
/CLAUDE.md                      @TECH-LEAD
/.gemini/                       @TECH-LEAD

# CI workflows — changing the law's enforcement requires the same review
# as changing the law
/.github/workflows/             @TECH-LEAD

# Dependency manifests — new dependencies are a Human Gate
package.json                    @TECH-LEAD